data.description: Welcome home to this exquisitely renovated waterfront property nestled on Todds Creek. This 1700 sq ft ranch-style home, with its three bedrooms and two baths, is the epitome of comfort and luxury. The home features an attached 1-car garage and a meticulously crafted custom kitchen, featuring maple toned solid wood cabinets, a brand-new café fridge, dishwasher, and an ILVE gas range, add a touch of elegance to this cozy abode. The bay window in the kitchen offers breathtaking views of the sunset. Imagine yourself on your expansive 5-acre land, overlooking 272 ft of pristine waterfront. The riprap-protected shoreline ensures the property's safety and integrity. The large 16 X 16 screened porch is an ideal place to enjoy the breeze, while the rear aggregate patio invites you to unwind around a warm fire. Avid anglers will delight in the convenience of electricity, running water, and lights at the pier, making fishing a breeze. The dock boasts 5-6 ft of deep water at high tide, providing easy access to the East River and the Chesapeake Bay. This home is more than just a property; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of paradise. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty of this waterfront retreat.
